casebody.data:
Larry Silberberg, as Trustee under an Agreement between Flo Luxenberg and Others, and Eagle Converting Company, a Partnership, Appellant, v. Ruth Lipton, Individually and as Executrix of Conrad Lipton, Deceased, Respondent, et al., Defendants.

(Republish.)

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the respondent. No opinion. The date for the examination to proceed shall be fixed in the order. Settle order on notice. Present — Dore, J, P., Cohn, Callahan, Van Voorhis and Breitel, JJ. [See ante, p. 959.]
